    left join
        plafonds p1_0 
            on p1_0.id=cd1_0.plafond_id 
            and (p1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        users u1_0 
            on u1_0.id=cd1_0.user_id 
            and (u1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        (user_roles r1_0 
    join
        roles r1_1 
            on r1_1.id=r1_0.role_id) 
        on u1_0.id=r1_0.user_id 
        and ( r1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    where
        cd1_0.user_id=?

        )

        p1_1.is_deleted,
        p1_1.updated_at,
        p1_1.updated_by 
    from
        role_permissions p1_0 
    join
        permissions p1_1 
            on p1_1.id=p1_0.permission_id 
    where
        p1_0.role_id=? 
        and (
            p1_1.is_deleted = 0
        )

    select
        distinct u1_0.id,
        u1_0.created_at,
        u1_0.created_by,
        u1_0.email,
        u1_0.fcm_token,
        u1_0.is_active,
        u1_0.is_deleted,
        u1_0.password,
        r1_0.user_id,
        r1_1.id,
        r1_1.created_at,
        r1_1.created_by,
        r1_1.is_deleted,
        r1_1.name,
        p1_0.role_id,
        p1_1.id,
        p1_1.code,
        p1_1.created_at,
        p1_1.created_by,
        p1_1.is_deleted,
        p1_1.updated_at,
        p1_1.updated_by,
        r1_1.updated_at,
        r1_1.updated_by,
        u1_0.updated_at,
        u1_0.updated_by,
        u1_0.username 
    from
        users u1_0 
    left join
        (user_roles r1_0 
    join
        roles r1_1 
            on r1_1.id=r1_0.role_id) 
        on u1_0.id=r1_0.user_id 
        and ( r1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        (role_permissions p1_0 
    join
        permissions p1_1 
            on p1_1.id=p1_0.permission_id) 
        on r1_1.id=p1_0.role_id 
        and ( p1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    where
        (
            u1_0.is_deleted = 0
        ) 
        and u1_0.username=?

        cd1_0.created_at,
        cd1_0.created_by,
        cd1_0.date_of_birth,
        cd1_0.full_name,
        cd1_0.house_status,
        cd1_0.is_deleted,
        cd1_0.is_male,
        cd1_0.job,
        cd1_0.marital_status,
        cd1_0.national_id,
        cd1_0.phone_number,
        cd1_0.place_of_birth,
        p1_0.id,
        p1_0.created_at,
        p1_0.created_by,
        p1_0.is_deleted,
        p1_0.max_amount,
        p1_0.max_tenor,
        p1_0.name,
        p1_0.next_plafond_limit,
        p1_0.order_number,
        p1_0.updated_at,
        p1_0.updated_by,
        cd1_0.religion,
        cd1_0.remain_plafond,
        cd1_0.salary,
        cd1_0.updated_at,
        cd1_0.updated_by,
        cd1_0.workplace,
        cd1_0.zip_code,
        u1_0.email,
        u1_0.fcm_token,
        u1_0.is_active,
        u1_0.is_deleted,
        u1_0.password,
        r1_0.user_id,
        r1_1.id,
        r1_1.created_at,
        r1_1.created_by,
        r1_1.is_deleted,
        r1_1.name,
        r1_1.updated_at,
        r1_1.updated_by,
        u1_0.updated_at,
        u1_0.updated_by,
        u1_0.username 
    from
        users u1_0 
    left join
        customer_details cd1_0 
            on u1_0.id=cd1_0.user_id 
            and (cd1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        plafonds p1_0 
            on p1_0.id=cd1_0.plafond_id 
            and (p1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        (user_roles r1_0 
    join
        roles r1_1 
            on r1_1.id=r1_0.role_id) 
        on u1_0.id=r1_0.user_id 
        and ( r1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    where
        u1_0.id=? 
        and (
            u1_0.is_deleted = 0
        )

    select
        p1_0.role_id,
        p1_1.id,
        p1_1.code,
        p1_1.created_at,
        p1_1.created_by,
        p1_1.is_deleted,
        p1_1.updated_at,
        p1_1.updated_by 
    from
        role_permissions p1_0 
    join
        permissions p1_1 
            on p1_1.id=p1_0.permission_id 
    where
        p1_0.role_id=? 
        and (
            p1_1.is_deleted = 0
        )

    join
        roles r1_1 
            on r1_1.id=r1_0.role_id 
    where
        r1_0.user_id=?

            r1_1.is_deleted = 0
        )

        cd1_0.phone_number,
        cd1_0.place_of_birth,
        p1_0.id,
        p1_0.created_at,
        p1_0.created_by,
        p1_0.is_deleted,
        p1_0.max_amount,
        p1_0.max_tenor,
        p1_0.name,
        p1_0.next_plafond_limit,
        p1_0.order_number,
        p1_0.updated_at,
        p1_0.updated_by,
        cd1_0.religion,
        cd1_0.remain_plafond,
        cd1_0.salary,
        cd1_0.updated_at,
        cd1_0.updated_by,
        cd1_0.workplace,
        cd1_0.zip_code,
        pb1_0.email,
        pb1_0.fcm_token,
        pb1_0.is_active,
        pb1_0.is_deleted,
        pb1_0.password,
        pb1_0.updated_at,
        pb1_0.updated_by,
        pb1_0.username 
    from
        loan_status_histories sh1_0 
    left join
        users pb1_0 
            on pb1_0.id=sh1_0.performed_by_id 
            and (pb1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        customer_details cd1_0 
            on pb1_0.id=cd1_0.user_id 
            and (cd1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        plafonds p1_0 
            on p1_0.id=cd1_0.plafond_id 
            and (p1_0.is_deleted = 0) 
    where
        sh1_0.loan_id=?

    select
        distinct u1_0.id,
        u1_0.created_at,
        u1_0.created_by,
        u1_0.email,

        u1_0.is_active,
        u1_0.is_deleted,
        u1_0.password,
        r1_0.user_id,
        r1_1.id,
        r1_1.created_at,
        r1_1.created_by,
        r1_1.is_deleted,
        r1_1.name,
        p1_0.role_id,
        p1_1.id,
        p1_1.code,
        p1_1.created_at,
        p1_1.created_by,
        p1_1.is_deleted,
        p1_1.updated_at,
        p1_1.updated_by,
        r1_1.updated_at,
        r1_1.updated_by,
        u1_0.updated_at,
        u1_0.updated_by,
        u1_0.username 
    from
        users u1_0 
    left join
        (user_roles r1_0 
    join
        roles r1_1 
            on r1_1.id=r1_0.role_id) 
        on u1_0.id=r1_0.user_id 
        and ( r1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    left join
        (role_permissions p1_0 
    join
        permissions p1_1 
            on p1_1.id=p1_0.permission_id) 
        on r1_1.id=p1_0.role_id 
        and ( p1_1.is_deleted = 0) 
    where
        (
            u1_0.is_deleted = 0
        ) 
        and u1_0.username=?

        )
